USAGE: @G{shield} tenant [--members] @Y{NAME-OR-UUID}

  Show Information for a single SHIELD Tenant.

  Each SHIELD Core defines one or more tenants, each with their own
  set of cloud storage configurations, retention policies, data systems,
  and backup jobs.

  @Y{NOTE:} This command is only available to @R{SHIELD Site Managers}.

@B{Options:}

  --members      List all users who have been granted access to this
                 Tenant, and identify their role within.

